======
ws_ui
======

A simple tui tool to communicate with websocket.

Install
=======

.. code::

    pip install ws-ui


Usage
======

Just call the command with websocket url.

.. code::

    $ ws-ui ws://localhost:8080/ws/


.. code:: 

    Enter msg and press Enter to send message                                                     

